Projects

The Good Space

This website was inspired by the COVID-19 pandemic and the simplicity of Craigslist. The name of the project is a riff off of "The Good Place" show.

I wanted to create a space for members of the community to reach out for help and receive help.

Tech Stack:

Backend: Ruby on Rails, Frontend: React.js, API: React Google Maps, Database: PostgreSQL, Styling: Bootstrap

Plantify

Plantify is a website for plant lovers (or killers) that allow users to keep track of their plant care needs and reminds them when to water the plants.

Video Demo

Backend + Frontend: Ruby on Rails, HTML, CSS

Database: MySQL
